4100:She slumped over onto the sofa and lay there, unmoving.[%p]
4200:Had she fallen asleep? Had she finally run out of steam?[%p]
4300:I sighed in relief as the tension left my body. I hadn't had a moment's relief while she was staring at me, but now I could finally get a little rest.[%p]
