5300:I'd thought she was working for Shogun, too.[%p]
5400:But she was the one who'd made me think that. She was the one who'd tricked me. Lied to me. So even if I raped her, or made her endure all kinds of sexy punishments, she wouldn't have the right to complain.[%p]
